Subcommands:
  create <name>|--latest [label]                Snapshot current changes (default label: checkpoint-<epoch>)
  list   <name>|--latest                        List all checkpoints for the container
  revert <name>|--latest <ref>                  Restore a checkpoint (discards current changes)
  fork   <name>|--latest <new-name> [label]     Create a new agent from a checkpoint snapshot

Options:
  --latest    Target the most recently started container
  -h, --help  Show this help

Examples:
  agent checkpoint create my-task before-refactor
  agent checkpoint list my-task
  agent checkpoint revert my-task before-refactor
  agent checkpoint fork my-task my-task-v2 before-refactor
  agent checkpoint create --latest
  agent checkpoint list --latest
EOF
}

